&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Participants will discuss contemporary topics around Black Germans, and brainstorm how to use short films, music videos and short non-fiction texts by Black Germans as supplements in class. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400;&quot;&gt;Participants will be able to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400;&quot;&gt;identify historical and current facts about Black Germans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400;&quot;&gt; employ vocabulary and topics about racism in Germany.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400;&quot;&gt;compare their knowledge of other non-white musicians/filmmakers in Germany&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400;&quot;&gt;reorganize the information provided into what they might need for their classrooms. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
